(157, 10, 177, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 2, '•	The applicants should have experience in the following area(s):\r\nAccounting and Finance', 'The applicants should have experience in the following area(s): Accounts, Tax (VAT/ Customs Duty/ Income Tax), Cash Management\r\nGood command over computer, especially in MS Office & e-mail\r\nShould have strong analytical skills \r\nSelf-motivated and organized individual \r\nHardworking with good communication skill \r\nCapable of Operate Accounting Software.', 2, 22, 28, 1, '2021-08-30 05:19:54', '2021-08-30 05:19:54'),
