(161, 10, 181, 'Public or Nation University', 'Masters in Finance or Accounting from any reputed public or private University.\r\nMBA/M.Com in Finance or Accounting from any reputed institution with CMA partly qualified or CA(CC) partly qualifies will get preference.', NULL, 0, 5, 'The applicants should have experience in the following area(s):\r\nACCA or acca part qualified preferred, Accountant, Accounting and Finance, Accounting and VAT', 'Age 30 to 45 years\r\nOnly males are allowed to apply\r\nThe applicants should have clear knowledge in the following area(s): Accounts, Finance, Audit, Tax (Vat/Custom Duty/Income Tax & relevant jobs.', 0, 28, 35, 1, '2021-08-31 05:04:03', '2021-08-31 05:06:31'),
