(166, 10, 186, 'Public or Nation University,', 'PGD HRM will be given preference.', NULL, 0, 10, 'The applicants should have experience in the following area(s):\r\nHRM, Planning Monitoring Evaluation Learning', 'Age 35 to 55 years\r\nThe applicants should have experience in General HR.\r\nAt least 10 years of experience in development sector with minimum 2 years in a leading position.\r\nExperience in project planning, monitoring and evaluation.\r\nDemonstrable lateral thinking and problem-solving abilities.\r\nMust be knowledgeable about Labor Law and Compliance.\r\nEfficiency in computer operation and digital data collection tools.\r\nExcellent communication and presentation skills with good command over English.\r\nAbility to flourish with minimal guidance, be proactive, and handle uncertainty.\r\nA strong team player, with the ability to work effectively with others to achieve results, with strong advisory/ facilitation skills.', 2, 35, 55, 1, '2021-08-31 05:28:18', '2021-08-31 05:28:18'),
(167, 10, 187, 'Public or Nation University,', 'Bachelor degree in any discipline\r\nMinimum Graduate (we don\'t bother from which discipline you have been graduated from)\r\nSkills Required: Bangla and english typing Skills, Computer Literacy Fluency in English speaking and writing', NULL, 0, 2, 'The applicants should have experience in the following area(s):\r\nAbility to Work Under Pressure, Administration\r\nThe applicants should have experience in the following business area(s):\r\nAirline, Computer Hardware/Network Companies, Design/Printing/Publishing, E-commerce\r\nFreshers are also encouraged to apply.', 'Age 22 to 27 years\r\nOnly males are allowed to apply\r\nEx Cadets from BMA or Lieutenant/ Captain are encouraged to apply.\r\nMust be good looking, tall & well groomed.\r\nMust have corporate culture as the office will be at Gulshan on a prestigious with the prestigious Group.\r\nResearch skills & Self-motivation.\r\nOnly Males Who are Ready to Work for Longer Hours Are Allowed to Apply', 0, 22, 28, 1, '2021-08-31 05:33:35', '2021-08-31 05:33:35'),
