(169, 10, 189, 'Public or Nation University,', 'CS (Chartered Secretary) with BBA & MBA major in Management, HR, Accounting or Finance from any reputed public or private university.', NULL, 0, 3, 'The applicants should have experience in the following area(s):\r\nCompany Secretary, Company Secretary/ Share Operation\r\nThe applicants should have experience in the following business area(s):\r\nGarments, Textile', 'Age at least 25 years\r\nOnly males are allowed to apply\r\nInstitute of Chartered Secretaries of Bangladesh (ICSB) certified professional experiences as Company Secretary in Listed Company with 03 years work experience.', 0, 25, 35, 1, '2021-08-31 05:36:10', '2021-08-31 05:36:10'),
(170, 11, 190, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 'The applicants should have experience in the following area(s):\r\nIncome Tax and VAT, TDS, VAT and tax regulations\r\nThe applicants should have experience in the following business area(s):\r\nAudit Firms /Tax Consultant, Financial Consultants, NGO, Insurance, Investment/Merchant Banking', 'Both males and females are allowed to apply\r\nThe job would require coverage of the below matters:\r\nEntry strategy from a tax and regulatory perspective\r\nOptimum use of corporate tax incentives in proposed business activities\r\nTax implications on profit and dividend repatriation\r\nAdvising on withholding tax obligations on payments\r\nObtaining no-objection certificates\r\nAssistance in filing various Tax Returns\r\nAssistance during Tax audit by revenue authorities\r\nCorporate tax litigation assistance, including representation services\r\nRegulatory services\r\nCorporate secretarial services', 2, 32, 40, 1, '2021-08-31 05:38:49', '2021-08-31 05:38:49'),
