t;,serif\">Self-Assessment with Independent External Validations of the internal audit function in accordance with IIA Professional Standards</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Advice and consultation on internal control issues, control design, and risk-reduction strategies.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 1, '2021-08-30 05:00:13', '2021-08-30 05:00:13'),
(4, 3, 'Company Secretarial Services', 'company-secretarial-services', 'Company Secretarial Services', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Services involve in this area is as follows:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-roman\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Drafting the Memorandum &amp; Articles of Association of Limited Liability Company regulated by the Companies Act-1994;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Maintaining the formalities for formation of a Limited Liability Company with the Registrar of Joint Stock Companies &amp; Firms;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Preparation of Notice &amp; Minutes of Annual General Meeting and maintaining the formalities for holding the AGM and submission the necessary papers and documents with the Registrar of Joint Stock Companies and Firms; </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Preparation of Notice &amp; Minutes of Board of Directors Meeting and maintaining the formalities for holding the Board meeting and submission the necessary papers &amp; documents with the Registrar of Joint Stock Companies &amp; Firms;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Maintaining the Notice Book, Minutes Book of Different Meeting like Annual General Meeting, Board of Directors Meeting &amp; any other meeting (if any); </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Handling the issue of change of Directors, Share Transfer, change of Register office, Change of Articles of Association, Allotment of Share, Change of Share Capital etc.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Processing the Tax Payers Identification Number.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Preparation and Submission of Income tax Return</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Yearly Tax Assessment done of the Liaison office.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Preparation of the Quarterly Accounts and submit this with Board of Investment, Bangladesh Bank, Tax Authority.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>', 1, '2021-08-30 05:01:14', '2021-08-30 05:01:14'),
(5, 4, 'Human Resource Payroll management', 'human-resource-payroll-management', 'Human Resource Payroll management', '<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Preparation of Monthly Payroll.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Preparation of Payment advice &amp; Send the institution to the Bank.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Structuring the gross salary in view of maximum tax benefit of the Company &amp; Employee.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Computation of Tax Liability.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Deduction of Tax deduction at source &amp; Deposit in the govt. Treasury.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Advice Client on the Tax deduction at source and VAT deduction at Source from various types of expenditure like supplier and others service provider.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>', 1, '2021-08-30 05:01:43', '2021-08-30 05:01:43'),
(6, 5, 'Tax Consultancy Services', 'tax-consultancy-services', 'Tax Consultancy Services', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Services involve in this area is to advise clients in respect of personal &amp; Corporate Tax &amp; VAT related issues and other specific services listed below:&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-roman\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Playing Role in the Tax Department as Authorized Representative and explain the return of income before the Assessing Authority.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">To get Assessment done by the Deputy Commissioner of Taxes</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Preparation of Paper &amp; Documents including grounds of Appeal in case of an Assessee aggrieved by the order passed by the Deputy Commissioner of Taxes.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">To attend in favor of Assessee as Authorized Representative before the Commissioner of Taxes (Appeal), Appellate Tribunal.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">To Communicate the Client Rules &amp; Regulation of Value Added Tax (VAT) </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Assisting the client in getting approval Tax Holiday facilities from National Board of Revenue.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">To communicate clients Rules Regarding Advances Taxes, Tax deduction at source Double Taxation Relief.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Rules &amp; Regulation regarding Special Tax Relief Scheme for industrial set- up for example sanctioning Accelerate Depreciation and initial depreciation in lieu of Tax Holiday Facility.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Tax Planning for forthcoming year in respect of Individual &amp; Company.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Processing of Tax exemption &amp; Tax clearance certificate for foreign nationals.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>', 1, '2021-08-30 05:02:59', '2021-08-30 05:02:59'),
(7, 7, 'VAT Consultancy Service', 'vat-consultancy-service', 'VAT Consultancy Service', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">The VAT must be submitted within the time specified by the Act, which includes:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">For goods manufactured, produced, imported, purchased, acquired or produced the VAT must be paid when:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">Delivery and supply of goods has been made;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">Invoice has been issued;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">Goods used for personal reasons or supplied for the use of others;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">Payment received in full or part.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">For taxable services, VAT will be paid when:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">Service is rendered;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">Invoice is issued;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">Payment in full or part has been received.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">In case of services received from beyond the geographical area of Bangladesh, VAT needs to be paid when payment is made in part or full.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#090e1d\">In the presence of a VAT Consultant, a businessperson needs not to be concerned about any VAT related issues as those are being dealt by the consultant with expertise and in a professional manner. A VAT consultant can provide precise information and advice regarding the procedure of registration, amount&nbsp; &nbsp;of VAT that needs to be paid and ensures all paper works relating to VAT and other taxes are up to date, thereby, minimizing chance of any error. &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>', 1, '2021-08-30 05:04:06', '2021-08-30 05:04:06');

