nternal and external evaluation (baseline, midterm and end-line).\r\nEnsure quality of organizational monitoring and evaluation system by introducing new tools and techniques.\r\nArrange quarterly follow-up meeting for monitoring & evaluation follow-up and learning.\r\nCapture the learning and achievements through proper documentations and ensure the quality of all publications.\r\nEnsure compliances of CSS PMEL manual.\r\nProvide necessary feedback and support to projects for better performance based on monitoring and evaluation findings.', 0, 'Dhaka', 4, 0, 0, 'Negotiable', 'After being permanent upon successful completion of probation period (six months), other benefits will be offered as per the organizational policy i.e. provident fund, gratuity, festival bonus, yearly increment, staff insurance (kormi Bima), medical allowance (Kormi Sohayota Tohobil) etc.', 1, '2021-08-31 05:28:18', '2021-08-31 05:28:18'),
(168, 10, 187, 2, NULL, 'This is full time job , but you`ve to perform .', 'Managing & organizing both formal + informal meetings and appointments of the Managing Director & CEO on a daily basis.\r\nWhenever instructed Organize and setup scheduled virtual meetings for the Managing Director & CEO on different online platforms such as Zoom, Google Meet, Microsoft Teams, Skype etc on a regular basis.\r\nCoordinate the meeting files & update Managing Director & CEO, scheduling and calendaring next meetings, identifying, inviting and confirming participants, facility arrangements where required.\r\nEnsure the Managing Director & CEO is fully briefed on, or prepared for engagements he is involved.\r\nReminding the Managing Director & CEO of important tasks and deadlines.\r\nCapability to Draft business letters, emails, personal correspondence, and provide other administrative assistance regarding documentation to the Managing Director & CEO..\r\nManage the Managing Director & CEO office ensuring the proper documentation of personal and business files, record keeping and maintaining confidentiality.\r\nPreparing travel arrangements including visa, ticketing, transportation and hotel reservation for the Managing Director & CEO both domestic and international travels.\r\nFilter general information, queries, phone calls and invitations to the Managing Director & CEO by redirecting or taking forward such contact as appropriate\r\nCoordinate with management team, other departments and all wings of the group as per requirement or instruction provided by Managing Director & CEO.\r\nProvide cover when necessary for Reception duties.\r\nPerform any other tasks assigned by the management.', 0, 'Anywhere in Bangladesh', 4, 0, 0, 'Compensation & Other Benefits As per company policy.', 'Festival Bonus: 2\r\nYou\'ll get all the benefits after passing the probation period & depends on your performance', 1, '2021-08-31 05:33:35', '2021-08-31 05:33:35'),
(169, 11, 188, 1, NULL, 'This is full time job , but you`ve to perform .', 'Managing & organizing both formal + informal meetings and appointments of the Managing Director & CEO on a daily basis.\r\nWhenever instructed Organize and setup scheduled virtual meetings for the Managing Director & CEO on different online platforms such as Zoom, Google Meet, Microsoft Teams, Skype etc on a regular basis.\r\nCoordinate the meeting files & update Managing Director & CEO, scheduling and calendaring next meetings, identifying, inviting and confirming participants, facility arrangements where required.\r\nEnsure the Managing Director & CEO is fully briefed on, or prepared for engagements he is involved.\r\nReminding the Managing Director & CEO of important tasks and deadlines.\r\nCapability to Draft business letters, emails, personal correspondence, and provide other administrative assistance regarding documentation to the Managing Director & CEO..\r\nManage the Managing Director & CEO office ensuring the proper documentation of personal and business files, record keeping and maintaining confidentiality.\r\nPreparing travel arrangements including visa, ticketing, transportation and hotel reservation for the Managing Director & CEO both domestic and international travels.\r\nFilter general information, queries, phone calls and invitations to the Managing Director & CEO by redirecting or taking forward such contact as appropriate\r\nCoordinate with management team, other departments and all wings of the group as per requirement or instruction provided by Managing Director & CEO.\r\nProvide cover when necessary for Reception duties.\r\nPerform any other tasks assigned by the management.', 0, 'Dhaka', 4, 0, 0, NULL, 'Festival Bonus: 2\r\nYou\'ll get all the benefits after passing the probation period & depends on your performance', 1, '2021-08-31 05:34:04', '2021-08-31 05:34:04'),
(170, 10, 189, 2, NULL, 'Prepare board meeting minutes to register a new company\r\nPrepare Memorandum And Article of Association\r\nPrepare required forms to approve new company from government', 'Prepare board meeting minutes to register a new company\r\nPrepare Memorandum And Article of Association\r\nPrepare required forms to approve new company from government\r\nQuestionable of any compliance of the company\r\nAppoint directors of the company\r\nChange directors of the company\r\nAttend and arrange Annual General Meeting\r\nArrange any board meeting resolution\r\nIncrease share of the company\r\nPrepare papers to apply of public listing company\r\nUpdate to the employer about listing rules and regulations\r\nKeep relations with employers, employees, auditors, government and non-government bodies.', 0, 'Rajshahi', 4, 0, 0, 'Negotiable', 'Mobile bill, Provident fund\r\nLunch Facilities: Partially Subsidize\r\nSalary Review: Yearly\r\nFestival Bonus: 2\r\nAs per company policy.', 1, '2021-08-31 05:36:10', '2021-08-31 05:36:10'),
(171, 11, 190, 1, NULL, NULL, 'The tasks, roles and responsibilities concerned with the job will include the following:\r\nEnd to end execution of client deliverables ensuring quality and timeliness\r\nIT assessment and reassessment\r\nIT/ TDS returns and compliances\r\nTax provisioning\r\nAdvisory and compliances on DTAAs (Outbound and Inbound)\r\nInteraction with Government and Regulatory authorities\r\nAssist clients with appeals and representations in front of the Tribunal and IT commissioner\r\nSeeking opinions from experts', 0, 'Dhaka.', 4, 0, 0, NULL, 'T/A, Mobile bill, Tour allowance, Medical allowance, Performance bonus, Profit share, Provident fund, Weekly 2 holidays\r\nLunch Facilities: Partially Subsidize\r\nSalary Review: Yearly\r\nFestival Bonus: 2\r\nAs per company policy.', 1, '2021-08-31 05:38:49', '2021-08-31 05:38:49'),
(172, 10, 191, 1, NULL, 'Assistant General Manager/Deputy General Manager - Internal Audit (Land Division) is responsible for supporting the Head of Internal Audit in all internal audit activities- audit planning, development of audit methodology, guidelines, policies and procedures to execute audit activities efficiently and perform financial & operational audits of the company`s business units and outsourced operations in line with Standards of Internal Audit. He is also responsible for reviewing & reporting the VAT and Tax source deduction & return submission compliance as per current regulations and reviewing the registrations, ERC, IRC, Trade licenses renewals, agreement/deed, refund policy to ensure accuracy and reviewing the financial statement of all units of the group in connection with relevant compliance. In addition, he need to make recommendations to improve business controls, efficiency and compliance to fortify that the audit work is appropriately executed.', 'Prepare internal audit operations plan and submit to HOD.\r\nVerified the Feasibility compliances before taking each land.\r\nVerified & Report on Procurement and Payments against land as per policy and AOP.\r\nVerified & Report on Sales and Collection against land as per policy and AOP as well as reconciliation with Bank Statement.\r\nVerified & report on the Financial Statement compliance of Land Unit.\r\nVerified & check the VAT and Tax source deduction & return submission compliance as per current Finance Act/VAT Act-1991/ Income Tax Ordinance & Rules-1984 etc.\r\nObtain, analyze and evaluate accounting documentation, previous reports, data, flowcharts etc.\r\nLand site visit physically for checking bills of Sand filling, Land development, Security etc.\r\nVerified the statutory documents related with each land.\r\nPrepare and present reports that reflect audit\'s results and document process.\r\nCheck internal administrative & accounting controls to safeguard assets & ensure compliance with laws & regulations.\r\nInvestigate occurrences of fraud, embezzlement, theft, waste and recommends controls to prevent or detect such occurrences.\r\nPerform audit & identify risk management and control management over operations\' effectiveness, financial reliability and compliance with all applicable directives and regulations\r\nReview the existing operational flows and business activities to ensure their efficiency and effectiveness.\r\nPrepare comprehensive Audit findings report with recommendations for development.\r\nContribute to the design and development of Internal Control Tools and Processes.\r\nConduct periodic internal audit of project outside Dhaka when required.\r\nReview project Accounts, Asset Management, store management system and submit development plan.\r\nSound knowledge on IFRS/IAS/ISA.', 0, 'Dhaka', 0, 45000, 65000, 'Negotiable', 'Mobile bill, Medical allowance, Insurance, Gratuity\r\nSalary Review: Yearly\r\nFestival Bonus: 2\r\nEarn Leave, Yearly Increment and others benefits as per company policy', 1, '2021-08-31 05:39:27', '2021-08-31 05:39:27'),
(173, 11, 192, 1, NULL, 'Looking for those candidates who have good knowledge & experience to work all types of VAT & Tax related works of a company.', 'Regular follow-up VAT & Tax related works of the Company.\r\nManage all corporate VAT & Tax and filings in the right manner.\r\nPrepare & submit monthly VAT return & others related documents.\r\nEnsure submit of income Tax & VAT in due time.\r\nMaintaining & preparing all kind of vouchers, cash book, bank book, bill register, general ledger & different registers related to finance & accounts.\r\nMonitoring & checking Petty Cash Payment, Bank Payment, Journal Voucher, different bills, invoices & books of accounts & sales Statement.\r\nCo-ordinate with other department such as Production & Commercial.\r\nAny other responsibilities as and when assigned by the management.', 0, 'chittagong', 4, 0, 0, NULL, 'As per Company  System', 1, '2021-08-31 05:44:03', '2021-08-31 05:44:03'),
(174, 10, 193, 2, NULL, 'Looking for that candidates who have good knowledge & experience to work all types of VAT & Tax related works of a company.', 'Regular follow-up VAT & Tax related works of the Company.\r\nManage all corporate VAT & Tax and filings in the right manner.\r\nPrepare & submit monthly VAT return & others related documents.\r\nEnsure submit of income Tax & VAT in due time.\r\nAll others VAT & Tax related works.', 0, 'Dhaka', 4, 0, 0, 'Negotiable', 'As per company policy.', 1, '2021-08-31 05:48:48', '2021-08-31 05:48:48'),
(175, 10, 194, 2, NULL, 'Handle All Tax and Vat related issues of the Companies in time to time.\r\nResponsible for Submission of Tax return and able to face, hearing and finalization the assessment Of the return of each business unit.', 'Handle All Tax and Vat related issues of the Companies in time to time.\r\nResponsible for Submission of Tax return and able to face, hearing and finalization the assessment Of the return of each business unit.\r\nAlways Monitor on deduction of Tax and Vat at source and deposit The same as to the Govt. treasury on time.\r\nPrepare Tax & Vat Accounts and handle professionally Tax & Vat authorities independently.\r\nResponsible for efficient operation of Tax & Vat related accounting activities of the company.\r\nKeep Liaison and communication with Tax & Vat office.\r\nAssist Management in formatting corporate policy regarding Tax and Vat by providing technical support using Tax & Vat laws and regulations.', 0, 'Chitagong', 4, 0, 0, 'Negotiable', 'As per company policy', 1, '2021-08-31 05:51:40', '2021-08-31 05:51:40');

